 speakers:</b><b> </b></em>\r\n\r\nKickoff by Terry Bean, Executive Director at 313Dlove, CEO at uNetworked,\r\nFounder at Motor City Connect, Author, Speaker, Connector\r\n\r\nPanel discussion by:\r\nDenise M. Kiepper, Senior VP, Senior HR Business Partner – Fifth Third\r\nLaurie Bradley, President – ASG Renaissance\r\nJennifer L. Cherry, Senior VP and CDO – Marx Layne &amp; Co.\r\n\r\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>','Women Empowered','','inherit','open','open','','84-revision-v1','','','2013-09-02 17:49:22','2013-09-02 17:49:22','',84,'http://www.iaccusa.org/84-revision-33/',0,'revision','',0),
