viduals can nominate themselves for 4 different award categories. Link to the Nomination form and submission deadline can be found in the attachment to this email. Please note that if you would like IACC to nominate you or your company, we would be happy to do so for IACC members only once we have been provided the information requested in the form. IACC will be represented at the event and we look forward to seeing our members walk away with several of these awards.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.iaccusa.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Fifth-Third.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-896\" alt=\"Fifth Third\" src=\"http://www.iaccusa.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Fifth-Third-150x150.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><b>INDO-AMERICAN CHAMBER OF COMMERCE – USA</b></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #ff0000;\"><b>Upcoming Events:</b></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\" align=\"center\"><strong>Annual Golf Event</strong> - August 7, 2014 The Inns At St. John 8 AM - See event page</p>\r\nSeptember 10, 2014 – <b>Learn how to use LinkedIn effectively to meet your business needs with\r\n</b><strong>David Fischer, Senior Regional Marketing Director of Putnam Investments</strong> <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/davidfischer1sing\">https://www.linkedin.com/in/davidfischer1sing</a>\r\n\r\nOctober 16, 2014 – <b>Learn about Nutrition and how it can help you manage good health and stress\r\n</b><strong>Aarti Batavia MS, RDN, CLT, IFMCP. Founder of Nutrition and Wellness Consulting LLC</strong> <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/aartibatavia\">https://www.linkedin.com/in/aartibatavia</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Annual Banquet</strong> - November 13, 2014 Italian American Banquet Center of Livonia 6 PM - Shinola Inc President\r\n<strong>Keynote Speaker Jacques Panis President at Shinola  Topic: Manufacturing in Detroit\r\nFlye