	(1070,855,'2016-02-03 14:07:02','2016-02-03 14:07:02','<div>On behalf of IBS Global Consulting and the Indo-American Chamber of Commerce USA, I would like to invite you to attend a complimentary 1-hour webinar on <em><strong>\"Cultural Considerations for Successful Business Negotiations in India\"</strong></em> onWednesday, February 24, 2016 at 2:00 PM EST.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>The webinar will be presented by <strong>Barbara Boldt</strong> and will address important cultural factors that may affect your business negotiation strategy when doing business in India.  Ms. Boldt is an <em><strong>International Business Consultant</strong></em> and <em><strong>Cross-Cultural Trainer</strong> </em>at IBS Global Consulting, and specializes in helping entrepreneurial CEOs, senior executives, and global managers succeed in the complex and competitive world of global business.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>If you are thinking about doing business, <em>or already doing business</em>, in India, this webinar is for you!  For more information and to register, click <a href=\"http://www.ibsglobalconsulting.com/webinars.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>here</strong></a>.  We also invite you to join the conversation on Twitter <a href=\"https://www.twitter.com/ibsglobal\" target=\"_blank\">@ibsglobal</a>.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Regards,</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><strong>Tonya McNeal-Weary</strong>\r\nManaging Director\r\n\r\nIBS Global Consulting, Inc.\r\nGlobal Headquarters\r\n101 W. Big Beaver Road, Suite 1400\r\nTroy, MI 48084 USA\r\nDirect: <a href=\"tel:%2B1.248.581.0140%20ext%3A%20721\" target=\"_blank\">+1.248.581.0140 ext: 721</a>\r\nToll Free: <a href=\"tel:1.866.494.0281\" target=\"_blank\">1.866.494.0281</a>\r\nFax: <a href=\"tel:1.866.491.7137\" target=\"_blank\">1.866.491.7137</a>\r\nWeb: <a href=\"http://www.ibsglobalconsulting.com/\" target=\"_blank\">www.ibsglobalconsulting.<wbr />com</a></div>\r\n<div>\r\nInnovative Solutions to Move Your Business Forward</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>For any questions and to register please contact IACC-USA at <a href=\"mailto:admin@iaccusa.org\" target=\"_blank\">admin@iaccusa.org</a></div>','Webinar on \"Cultural Considerations for Successful Business Negotiations in India\"','','publish','closed','closed','','webinar-on-cultural-considerations-for-successful-business-negotiations-in-india','','','2016-02-03 14:07:02','2016-02-03 14:07:02','',0,'http://www.iaccusa.org/?post_type=tribe_events&#038;p=1070',0,'tribe_events','',0),
