	(1127,855,'2016-04-20 14:59:52','2016-04-20 14:59:52','Help Mayor Duggan to Grow Detroit\'s Young Talent\r\n\r\nAs the summer quickly approaches, we have an opportunity to Grow Detroit\'s Young Talent (<a href=\"https://app.nimble.com/api/v1/messages/tracking/click/549c6e109db07b1299efb062/5702c04f7443767f70e61483/5716eddd5d47ea394f4797e7/?redirect=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gdyt.org%2F\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=https://app.nimble.com/api/v1/messages/tracking/click/549c6e109db07b1299efb062/5702c04f7443767f70e61483/5716eddd5d47ea394f4797e7/?redirect%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.gdyt.org%252F&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1461249735387000&amp;usg=AFQjCNEPLDTlvF02cHhsRFj1PDj2Z4UvNA\">http://www.gdyt.org</a>).\r\n\r\nGive one or more young Detroiters the chance to learn from your expertise and experience.  While our GDYT participants help you to grow your business, you will help each of them to build the foundation for a career.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://app.nimble.com/api/v1/messages/tracking/click/549c6e109db07b1299efb062/5702c04f7443767f70e61483/5716eddd5d47ea394f4797e7/?redirect=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gdyt.org%2F\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=https://app.nimble.com/api/v1/messages/tracking/click/549c6e109db07b1299efb062/5702c04f7443767f70e61483/5716eddd5d47ea394f4797e7/?redirect%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.gdyt.org%252F&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1461249735387000&amp;usg=AFQjCNEPLDTlvF02cHhsRFj1PDj2Z4UvNA\">http://www.gdyt.org</a> shows the three steps to hire a young Detroiter this summer.\r\n1) Complete your registration for Grow Detroit Young Talent at <a href=\"https://app.nimble.com/api/v1/messages/tracking/click/549c6e109db07b1299efb062/5702c04f7443767f70e61483/5716eddd5d47ea394f4797e9/?redirect=http%3A%2F%2Fgdyt.org%2Femployers-supporters%2F\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=https://app.nimble.com/api/v1/messages/tracking/click/549c6e109db07b1299efb062/5702c04f7443767f70e61483/5716eddd5d47ea394f4797e9/?redirect%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fgdyt.org%252Femployers-supporters%252F&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1461249735387000&amp;usg=AFQjCNEoAUCeajSvvX2dnAYYds9GEKTR1Q\">http://gdyt.org/employers-<wbr />supporters/</a> <b>by <span class=\"aBn\" tabindex=\"0\" data-term=\"goog_92928947\"><span class=\"aQJ\">Friday, April 29</span></span>.\r\n</b>2) Provide a six week work experience for up to 20 hours per week\r\n2) Pay a 50:50 match sponsorship of $850 or a full sponsorship of $1,700.\r\nAlternatively, you can directly hire the young Detroiter.\r\n\r\nThe 2016 Grow Detroit’s Young Talent Program will run from <span class=\"aBn\" tabindex=\"0\" data-term=\"goog_92928948\"><span class=\"aQJ\">July 6th through August 26th</span></span>.\r\n\r\nGDYT will manage student recruitment, matching each young Detroiter to the right opportunity, payroll, work readiness training, and employer support.\r\n\r\nAssigned GDYT specialists will support each GDYT student throughout the summer.  This GDYT Youth Specialist will provide ongoing training throughout the summer and help each young person have a successful summer in the workplace.\r\n\r\nGDYT youth will receive bus passes to assist with transportation throughout the summer.\r\n\r\nWe look forward to any questions you might have and to your commitment to Grow Detroit’s Young Talent.\r\n\r\nThanks,\r\n\r\n-Jill Ford\r\n<a>(313) 887-0822</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.iaccusa.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/grow-detroits-young-talent.pdf\" rel=\"\">grow detroit\'s young talent</a>','Help Mayor Duggan to Grow Detroit\'s Young Talent - 2016','','publish','open','open','','help-mayor-duggan-to-grow-detroits-young-talent-2016','','','2016-04-20 15:01:26','2016-04-20 15:01:26','',0,'http://www.iaccusa.org/?p=1127',0,'post','',0),
