	(27454,1018,'last_name','Singh'),
	(27455,1018,'description',' The passionate and sensitive Guitarist Chakrapani Singh and his journeys as an individual through a whole gamut of emotions that reveals Truth, Beauty and Perfection towards MUSIC. The Veena in his hand produces the sweetest and most sensuous emotions that transcend one to the nether world. Chakrapani is truly a rare instrumentalist with an unique repertoire ranging from traditional, classical compositions on the slide guitar to his innovative, renditions on the Kachappi Veena. This maverick musician leaves every music lover spell bound with his flashes of unparalleled brilliance. Chakrapani\'s everlasting love for music is undoubtedly going to be a joyful journey. His unique style of playing amazed the audiences. Currently, Chakrapani is living in USA and performing solo concerts in support of audience appreciations.  \r\n\r\nAward winning Guitarist Chakrapani is a versatile musician. He is an innovative Kachhapi Veena player, who improved the tonal quality of his instrument by adding 35 more strings to make his playing more melodious. The variety of sweet musical sounds created with its amazing range of tonality and depth of expression. His unique style of playing and his innovative skills have brought honors to him with the prestigious awards like: “ Best World Music Performances”, \"The Virtuoso of Indian Classical Music\" in Mauritius, \"The Legend of Guitar\", \"3rd International Sardar Patel Award 2008\" and many more.\r\n\r\nThrough TACH, Chakrapani wants to promote Indian Classical Music. His motive is to aware music lovers with Music Education, Cultural Exchange Program, Fusion Music Collaboration, Seminar, Workshop, Music Competition, World Music Festival, Music Awareness, Audio – Video Production and Development of Traditional Cultural Harmony through TACH. \r\n\r\nChakrapani started TACH, LLC in Nevada, USA and then TACH International, Inc.He chooses state Nevada as he wants to expand his music awareness to the people who don’t get chance of hearing it easily. Everyone chooses big cities where people already aware about music. He is struggling to make aware the people of a small city but he is happy that he is trying to educate the people of a place where no one wants to start. He already started to educate the students of Washoe County, NV. Children get experience of Classical North Indian ragas (melodic forms from which the artist creates improvisations that expand upon the original melody), folk songs in the style of kirtan, and a fusion of Indian music with Western music. The audience participates at several points during the program to sing the notes of the scale in Indian Classical music, speaking tabla rhythms, and singing kirtan which express the joy of music and the oneness of humanity.\r\n\r\nThe local musicians are started getting warm welcome to take lessons and anytime knock his door to get aware of music culture. This humble artist has no life other then his dedication towards Music. But he is happy seeing that his passion towards music is started coming to the music lovers. His mainspring is after Nevada he will expand his music all over the USA.  Where artists come USA to just perform and earn big dollars and go back, Chakrapani Singh is devoting his life to bring awareness of Indian Classical Music without any expectations to the music lovers of USA.\r\n'),
